{"tid":2361333,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"叱咤最尾原來不像你預期 沈淪舊時打飛機 拒絕已境遷的心理","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:51:15.000Z","uid":86723,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9a70a5d3b42d0c28513d3db01ed299cef45527","tid":2361333,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"群眾喜歡姜濤麼<br />\n其實結果不隨我<br />\n我在我投入過的歌渡過<br />\n若有苦或痛也消磨<br />\n<br />\n其實我非新義安<br />\n還是八府的巡按<br />\n哪具有權力遏止歌熱播<br />\n若去糾纏你更囉嗦<br />\n<br />\n叱咤最尾原來不像你預期<br />\n沈淪舊時打飛機 拒絕已境遷的心理<br />\n都市一切亦撤離 方於廢墟裡玩味<br />\n年輪亦變遷 不管我或你"},{"pid":"cdbbcc784cb3e6ba20f620349b6cdaa09194366a","tid":2361333,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"鬼才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcb1a40dec691254b47a22e22f709f45c2580c4","tid":2361333,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"沈淪係咪打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4c1b28a3860d2ef3efb5a4e18232afbdea5296","tid":2361333,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcb1a40dec691254b47a22e22f709f45c2580c4","tid":2361333,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"沈淪係咪打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"速成狗打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然應該兩個都通"},{"pid":"e3586ca617a7a9dcbe858ebab407acb0be4f1493","tid":2361333,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdbbcc784cb3e6ba20f620349b6cdaa09194366a","tid":2361333,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"鬼才<img src=\"/assets/faces